Surf_Borisov (Beta 2)
 by Toaster aka. [NPZ] Mike <3 also known as Mike1097

Surf_Borisov is a Surf-Map, it works very good with the (R)ole(P)lay(G)ame-Mod.
It is given in order by the Multi-Gaming-Community NetPlayZone[NPZ].
The project is in the beta-status, that means that it is in a testing-phase.
Surf_Borisov will be Update to make it better and better.

Changelog:
__________
- Changed skybox
- Changed surfblock position
- Added jail-Open-Button in Jail
- Added jail-Kill-Effects
- Added jail-Bridge
- Fixed Pushes
- Fixed onRamp
- Fixed crash cushion size

***- Map is easier to surf!

Install Notes:
______________

- Open the surf_borisov_beta2.zip archive
- Extract the file into ../steam/steamapps/AccountName/Counter-Strike Source/cstrike/maps
- Start the game and play!
